  <h1>
   draw_light_get_ambient
  </h1>
  This function will return the current colour used for ambient lighting.
  <h4>
   Syntax:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">draw_light_get_ambient()
</code></pre>
  <h4>
   Returns:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml"><a href="../../../../../GameMaker_Language/GML_Reference/Drawing/Colour_And_Alpha/Colour_And_Alpha.htm">
 Colour
</a></code></pre>
  <h4>
   Example:
  </h4>
  <pre><code class="language-gml">light_col = draw_light_get_ambient();
</code></pre>
  The above code will get the current ambient light colour and store it in a variable.
 </body>
